@startuml
title Context Step Compilation - State Machine

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #F7F4ED
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam ArrowColor #30343B

[*] --> Collected : Mastra step input
Collected --> Grouped : group conversation turns
Collected --> Rejected : duplicate message id / invalid source
Grouped --> Merged : build + merge package revision
Merged --> Counted : system + tools + messages + reserves

Counted --> Planned : within budget
Counted --> Proposing : exceeds input budget
Proposing --> Selecting : strategies return candidates
Proposing --> Rejected : no candidate
Selecting --> Counted : apply candidate and re-count
Selecting --> Rejected : no progress / mandatory affected

Planned --> Materialized : immutable ContextPlan
Materialized --> Verified : provider-shaped prompt count
Verified --> Used : provider call allowed
Verified --> Rejected : final budget exceeded

Used --> Audited : bounded metrics
Rejected --> Audited : reason without prompt body
Audited --> [*]

state Collected #D8EAF1
state Grouped #D8EAF1
state Merged #DCE8C9
state Counted #F9D65C
state Proposing #F2D8D5
state Selecting #F2D8D5
state Planned #DCE8C9
state Materialized #DCE8C9
state Verified #E7DDF1
state Used #DCE8C9
state Rejected #F7C9B6
state Audited #E7DDF1

note right of Grouped
Only the last complete turn is mandatory.
Tool observations do not open a user turn.
end note

note right of Selecting
Strategies propose candidates.
The selector is replaceable; no fixed global action order.
end note

@enduml
